WEBVTT

00:03.107 --> 00:05.492
It's incredible news.

00:06.277 --> 00:07.703
Karen Klimsky...

00:08.487 --> 00:10.122
...said maybe.

00:10.406 --> 00:12.509
- She said maybe?
- Amazing, huh?

00:12.533 --> 00:14.177
She said maybe she'd
go out with you?

00:14.201 --> 00:15.961
She definitely said maybe.

00:19.165 --> 00:20.559
Well, so when will
you know for sure?

00:20.583 --> 00:21.685
Very soon.

00:21.709 --> 00:23.552
Look, Will,

00:23.669 --> 00:25.763
not to throw water on
this or anything...

00:27.423 --> 00:28.641
Will...

00:29.008 --> 00:30.652
What are you playing games for?

00:30.676 --> 00:33.238
I mean, that girl, uh,
Donna what's-her-name...

00:33.262 --> 00:34.281
- Sheingold.
- Yeah!

00:34.305 --> 00:35.824
If she's actually
interested in you...

00:35.848 --> 00:38.859
I mean, she practically follows you
around the cafeteria at lunch.

00:39.060 --> 00:41.288
Have you ever seen that show
<i>Let's Make a Deal,</i> Bay?

00:41.312 --> 00:42.205
- Yeah.
- Okay.

00:42.229 --> 00:44.416
Donna Sheingold is like that box

00:44.440 --> 00:46.376
Carol Merrill is
standing next to.

00:46.400 --> 00:49.244
Karen Klimsky is the
big deal of the day.

00:50.237 --> 00:51.131
Take the box, Will.

00:51.155 --> 00:53.467
Oh, that's... That's very
funny coming from you.

00:53.491 --> 00:55.552
I mean, not to be insensitive,
but talk about waiting around

00:55.576 --> 00:57.795
for something that's
not likely to happen.

00:57.828 --> 00:59.598
- It's been like a month, Bay.
- Yeah.

00:59.622 --> 01:01.757
So? You never know.

01:01.916 --> 01:04.061
Well, come on. At least
talk to another girl.

01:04.084 --> 01:06.971
- Look, Will, just mind your own...
- Guess who.

01:07.004 --> 01:08.023
What?

01:08.047 --> 01:10.099
Oh, come on. Don't tell
me you forgot already.

01:12.009 --> 01:13.987
- Kate!
- I knew you'd remember.

01:14.011 --> 01:15.271
Hey, Will.

01:15.846 --> 01:16.981
Oh!

01:17.431 --> 01:18.533
What... what are you doing?

01:18.557 --> 01:20.410
I can't believe I
pulled this off.

01:20.434 --> 01:23.487
I was dying to call you, but I
wanted it to be a surprise.

01:24.021 --> 01:26.541
See, they canceled classes for two
days for this conference thing.

01:26.565 --> 01:30.869
Anyway, all I could think about for a whole
week was seeing the look on your face.

01:32.947 --> 01:34.456
I missed you.

01:36.000 --> 01:42.074
-= www.OpenSubtitles.org =-

